<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* Light blue background */
            color: #333;
        }
        .dashboard-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff; /* White card */
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .profile-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .profile-pic {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid #1e90ff; /* Blue border */
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        .user-details {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .user-details h2 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #1e90ff; /* Blue text */
        }
        .user-details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="dashboard-container">
        <div class="profile-header">
            <img src="profile-pic-placeholder.jpg" alt="User Profile Picture" class="profile-pic">
            <div class="user-details">
                <h2><%=Fullname%></h2>
                <p>Email: <%= username%></p>
                <p>Phone: <%= phone%></p>
                <p>Location:<%= location%></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="additional-info">
            <h3>About</h3>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus lacinia odio vitae vestibulum vestibulum. Cras venenatis euismod malesuada.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>